# .engine-src is the release-workflow checkout of
# lexfrei/pogo-pvp-engine (see .github/workflows/release.yml). The
# Containerfile already receives that source via the `engine` named
# BuildKit context (COPY --from=engine), so sending it a second
# time through the default build context would bloat the builder
# layer. Local builds via scripts/build-image.sh use ENGINE_PATH
# and do not touch .engine-src/.
